snippet: Seventeen-year-old Madison Keys, a second-round winner Wednesday at the Australian Open, has been imposing herself on her elders with regularity this season.
abstract: Profile of 17-year-old tennis player Madison Keys, who has been imposing herself on her elders with regularity this season; Keys advanced to third round of Australian Open after quickly dispatching Tamira Paszek.
lead_paragraph: Seventeen-year-old Madison Keys, a second-round winner Wednesday at the Australian Open, has been imposing herself on her elders with regularity this season.
